'''Tallgrain''' was a crop grown in the [[Dorchess Valley]] on [[Pakrik Minor]]. [[Worm/Legends|Worms]] liked to build colonies in the roots of tallgrain, but as they could cause [[white-blight]], farmers continually worked to eradicate them. Tallgrain had a sour-musky aroma.<ref name="SotP">''[[Specter of the Past]]''</ref> Tallgrain was one of the top one hundred cash crops grown on [[Factory/Legends|factory]] [[Farm/Legends|farms]] in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]].<ref name="EGTD">''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref>

